Package: RpiR
Type: Package
Title: R interface to Raspberry Pi
Version: 0.1
Date: 2015-04-23
Authors@R: c(
  person(family="Trestle Technology, LLC", role="aut", email="cran@trestletechnology.net"),
  person("Jeff", "Allen", role="cre", email="cran@trestletechnology.net"))
Description: Builds on the wiringPi library to expose the various interactions
    possible via that utility through R, including digital reading/writing, and
    analog reading/writing.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
SystemRequirements: wiringPi
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.11.5)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
